How to use forth-mode.

   Key bindings:

'M-TAB'
'C-M-i'
'M-x completion-at-point'

     Attempt to complete the Forth word under point.

'C-M-f'
'M-x forward-sexp'

     Move forward across one balanced expression.

'C-M-b'
'M-x backward-sexp'

     Move backward across one balanced expression.


